The input dataset is located at https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1II8cT1qKEhA70GgNgkiItrIqGA00ebs0.
You should download input.zip which should be unzipped to the your filesystem. 
The structure of the directory should be
- input:
   - handwritten-signatures
     - sample_Signatures
        - forged
        - genuine
   - sigcomp-2009
     - forgeries
     - genuines
   - sigcomp-2009-training
     - forgeries
     - genuines
